import { Accordion, AccordionDetails, AccordionSummary, List, ListItem, ListItemButton, ListItemText, Typography } from "@mui/material"

function Accordions() {
  return (
    <>
    <Accordion>
        <AccordionSummary>
            <Typography>MERN</Typography>
        </AccordionSummary>
        <AccordionDetails>
            <Typography>MongoDB</Typography>
            <Typography>ReactJS</Typography>
            <Typography>ExpressJS</Typography>
            <Typography>MongoDB</Typography>

        </AccordionDetails>
    </Accordion>

{/* using list */}

    <Accordion>
        <AccordionSummary>
            <Typography>MERN</Typography>
        </AccordionSummary>
        <AccordionDetails>
            <List>
           
            <ListItem>
            <ListItemButton>
                <ListItemText primary='MongoDB'/>
            </ListItemButton>
        </ListItem>
        <ListItem>
            <ListItemButton>
                <ListItemText primary='ReactJS'/>
            </ListItemButton>
        </ListItem>
        <ListItem>
            <ListItemButton>
                <ListItemText primary='ExpressJS'/>
            </ListItemButton>
        </ListItem>
        <ListItem>
            <ListItemButton>
                <ListItemText primary='NodeJS'/>
            </ListItemButton>
        </ListItem>
            </List>

        </AccordionDetails>
    </Accordion>
      
    </>
  )
}

export default Accordions
